  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Sanitation mobile academy - mobile-based training and networking service for sanitation facilitators</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will create a mobile-based training and networking service, designed for sanitation facilitators for rural sanitation, similar to our Mobile Academy service. It will be piloted with sanitation facilitators in one state (possibly Bihar).  It will be a pilot project, but designed to scale, to support the government&#x2019;s Clean India Mission, which aims to scale up available communicators who conduct face-to-face interventions in communities from 250,000 existing communicators to 2 million.</narrative>
  </description>
